  "description": "Henan Shuanghui Investment & Development Co.,Ltd. engages in slaughtering, processing, and selling of meat products in China. The company is also involved in the breeding and sales of livestock and poultry; aquatic product processing; production and sales of feed; production and sales of PVDC films and food packaging materials, and other packaging materials; procurement of agricultural and sideline products; chemical product sales; and food industry investment. It also offers fresh pig products, canned meat, quick-frozen and packaged cooked meat products, edible animal fats, egg products, as well as technical consulting services, warehousing services, and catering services and management. The company was founded in 1998 and is headquartered in Luohe, China. Henan Shuanghui Investment & Development Co.,Ltd. is a subsidiary of Rotary Vortex Limited.",
